p: \bSuch an odd place to have built anything at all.\nI can't believe people can live out here.
\bWhy is there a temple here, of all places?
\rAh, our guest of honor has finally arrived.
\bWho on earth are you? What do you want?
\bYou're the one behind all of this, aren't you?
\bI... I've been researching.\nI know where the First Augur, Adam's Crystal came from.
\bI've looked into Persephone's past, which led me to Zenith and the Infernal Cult and what he can do.
\bAll of it ties back to you.
\bAre you cultists? Trying to catch Giratina?
\rNo. We might look the part, but we're anything but.
\bYou've been playing us like pawns! You've been playing ME like a pawn!
\rActually, I know you don't want to hear this, but...
\rYou weren't part of my plans. You're a minor nuisance at best. A bit part.
\rMy intention was for the Infernal Cult to eventually overthrow the First Augur and secure the crystal for me.
\rBut no, you just had to interfere, didn't you?
\rYou just had to play the edgy antihero, didn't you?
\bStay away from me. Don't make me break the crystal.
\rHah. Any more than you already have?
\r...but I'll let you go. Your shard is nearly useless to me without the other two.
\rAnd though I didn't care for you at first, you've slowly become useful.
